item.title: Please help!
item.dc:creator: @Armadyl_sol Armadyl sol
item.description:
@Armadyl_sol wrote:

you need to make sure your internet is allowing people to connect, there is a port people use, since you don’t know what i am talking about i am assuming your port is 43594 that is the default port, you need to make sure you have the port as an exception in your firewall, you will need two exceptions, name them both whatever you like, for one click the circle next to “tcp” and for the other do the exact same except instead of click the “tcp” circle click the one next to it named “udp” for both of them under port type in 43594
